node.text:
If you’re having “one of those days”, watch the Be Myself official music video on my YouTube (link in bio) 🙏🏻💖
•We ALL have “those days”. Where we don’t feel we are good enough, smart enough, pretty enough, skinny enough. Where we don’t feel that we “fit in” and feel like we are not worthy. I’m here to tell you that you are all SO loved and SO beautiful inside and out in your own unique ways. You ARE worthy. Be proud to say “I’m gonna be myself and I don’t wanna be nobody else”!
